title: *I'M NOT DEAD* Feeding The Family : Episode 30

embed.description: So I'm not dead, And I'm back now! I had a lot of hardware and other problems, The TL;DR version is all my recordings where dropping down to 17~ FPS and it was just completely unusable, I finally saved up to buy an SSD (960 evo M.2 :O ) and Pulled an all nighter to get this out, It's around 11 am when I uploaded this and I have work in 6 hours.
